text: Yongning Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Yitong Manchu Autonomous County, Jilin, China. , it has 5 residential communities and 3 villages under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Jilin == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Jilin Category:Yitong Manchu Autonomous County
